Job Description:

DISCOVER NEW HORIZONS WITH LIMÉ!

LIMÉ is a clothing, footwear, and accessories brand founded in 2008. Our stores are represented in Russia and the CIS, as well as online with worldwide delivery. Our success lies in well-coordinated teamwork, which enables us to create high-quality products that are in demand.

We are always happy to meet new people who share our values and positive attitude.

Our brand is opening a vacancy for a Commercial Manager / Visual merchandiser at Mega Mall.

Your responsibilities will include:

Ensuring a high level of customer service;

Organizing the visual merchandising process in the store in accordance with brand standards, sales analytics, and seasonal recommendations;

Preparing proposals for changes in the department’s assortment, delivery timelines, and product volumes;

Controlling store stock levels to ensure optimal representation of the collection by assortment and quantity in line with brand strategy;

