Developing commercial vision in working with the product and the store team’s merchandising;

Monitoring competitor products;

Training and developing the team.

We expect from you:

At least 1 year of experience in a similar role;

Skills in commercial product management (commercial visual merchandising);

Ability to work in multitasking mode and set priorities;

Strong result-oriented mindset;

Excellent communication, leadership, and organizational skills;

Knowledge of Armenian will be considered an advantage.

We offer:

Work schedule 5/2, flexible start of the working day, floating days off (including combined days off);

Competitive salary consisting of an hourly rate and a fixed store sales bonus (we do not have individual sales);

Opportunity to increase your income in the position with professional development;

Opportunity to recommend friends and receive a bonus;

